data.description: Check out this home located in Robinson ISD, sitting on a large corner lot! The home has three bedrooms, one bath, and one car garage. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances and granite countertops while the spacious backyard is great for entertaining. With some TLC, this home will make a great place to call home!
